WizardAttachmentForm is an ActionForm
    action is CreateFromWizard
    title is "SourcingEventAttachment"
    Layout
        single column
            SourcingEvent.RepresentativeText
                display as text
        paragraph
            Name
            Description
                use text area of 5 lines
        paragraph
            Attachment.File
                label is "Attachment"
        two column
            visible when (EligibleForCM)
                CMAttachment
                    label is "SendAttachmentToContractManagement"
            SupplierCanView
